<section id="body">
    <div class="jumbo-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1 text-white">
                    <p class="font-weight-bold header pb-3">PRICE</p>
                    <div class="d-flex py-4">
                        <p class="type mr-5">BUY</p>
                        <h1 class="font-weight-bold"><span class="currency pr-2">NGN</span><%= @bitcoin_buy_price %></h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex py-4">
                        <p class="type mr-5">SELL</p>
                        <h1 class="font-weight-bold"><span class="currency pr-2">NGN</span><%= @bitcoin_sell_price %></h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 order-1 order-lg-2">
                   <%= image_tag("bitcoins.png", :alt => "hero-image", :class => "img-fluid") %>     
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bitcoin-description">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1">
                    <%= image_tag("etherum-phone.png", :alt => "hero-image", :class => "img-fluid") %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 order-1 order-lg-2">
                    <h1 class="text-white header pb-3">Bitcoin <span class="text-muted coin-iso">BTC</span></h1>
                    <p class="text-white pt-4">
                        Bitcoin is a cryptocurrency which isnâ€™t managed by a bank or agency but in which transactions are recorded in the blockchain that is public and contains records of each and every transaction that takes place. The cryptocurrency is traded by individuals with cryptographic keys that act as wallets. Bitcoin was first invented in 2009 by an anonymous founder known as Satoshi Nakamoto. Bitcoins are moved in blocks every 10 minutes on a decentralized ledger that connects blocks into a coherent chain dating back to the first genesis block. It was originally described as a peer-to-peer electronic cash but the technology has evolved to emphasize being a settlement layer rather than a payment network. This has left integrated second layer solutions, like Lightning Network, to prioritize that use case. It has remained the largest cryptocurrency by market cap.
                    </p>
                    <%= link_to "https://www.coindesk.com/learn/bitcoin-101/what-is-bitcoin", class: "" do %>
                        Learn more <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right ml-2 text-white"></i>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h3 class="d-flex justify-content-center mb-5">Bitcoin businesses in Africa</h3>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="card shadow border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Buycoin Africa</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">The easiest way to buy and sell Bitcoin, Ethereum & Litecoin.</p>
                        <a href="https://buycoins.africa" class="btn btn-yellow">Visit</a>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="card shadow border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Bitpesa</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Bitpesa gives you access the Deepest BTC Liquidity in Africa.</p>
                        <a href="https://bitpesa.co" class="btn btn-yellow">Visit</a>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="card shadow border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Bithub Africa</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">A commercial Blockchain Accelerator driving Financial and Energy access.</p>
                        <a href="https://bithub.africa" class="btn btn-yellow">Visit</a>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
